Eurogroup approves third bailout for Greece
FXStreet (Córdoba) - Eurozone finance ministers approved new bailout for Greece with the first tranche agreed at €26 billion, DJ reports after the conclusion of Friday’s meeting in Brussels.Belgian Finance Minister said a deal was reached on Greece, with some additional measures, via Reuters.Dijsselbloem says last issues solved on Greek bailout and debt sustainability is possible without nominal haircuts.
